{"tid":2479125,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疫苗接種 ｜ 港多1人打科興後死 68歲婦針後死亡惟9日後才披露 15逝世13啪科興","createTime":"2021-04-07T14:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:41:22.000Z","uid":211167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"001107fa44476223cc0c20341caaefd9795f1582","tid":2479125,"uid":211167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"本港首宗接種武漢肺炎疫苗後死亡，是2月28日，即短短1個多月已有15人針後死，其中13人均打科興。政府一直不主動公佈首宗針後死，直至《蘋果》接獲死者友人求助率先踢爆後，事隔2日才披露。而12日內4宗死亡個案，全部都打過科興。不過武肺疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會認為，首2宗死亡與自身疾病有關，與打科興疫苗沒直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n雖然科興第三期臨床數據缺乏長者研究，更表明不建議長者接種；<strong><span class=\"red\">內地亦遲遲不為長者打科興，但香港卻安排長者打科興</span></strong>，自2月26日開打至今，針後不適送院大多是長者。不過港大醫學院助理院長、武肺疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會共同召集人孔繁毅解釋，即使科興不建議長者接種，亦不代表不同意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/MDNI4MIJ35GAPDEQUCWFCWTZXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FMDNI4MIJ35GAPDEQUCWFCWTZXM%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=821fb434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FMDNI4MIJ35GAPDEQUCWFCWTZXM%2F&h=c6d66f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/MDNI4MIJ35GAPDEQUCWFCWTZXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人條命真係低賤，連蝗國都未比老人家打科興，香港已經死左13個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解仲未輪到班「接左種」既高官死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif